name: Ubergraph Nonredundant
description: Ubergraph is an open-source graph database containing integrated ontologies, including GO, CHEBI, HPO, and Uberon’s anatomical ontology.
full_citation: Balhoff, J. P., Bayindir, U., Caron, A. R., Matentzoglu, N., Osumi-Sutherland, D., & Mungall, C. J. (2022, September 28). Ubergraph: integrating OBO ontologies into a unified semantic graph. ICBO 2022: International Conference on Biomedical Ontology (ICBO), Ann Arbor, Michigan, USA.
